{"id":267605,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/12/维权网-长沙维权人士刘华等人被批准逮捕（图）/","date":"2012-12-10T13:31:07Z","modified":"2012-12-10T13:31:07Z","title":"维权网 | 长沙维权人士刘华等人被批准逮捕（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）本网此前报道，因迎接在北京旅游被非法绑架回长沙的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>名上访维权人士，刘华、李颂明、曾武、邓生记等人因此被刑事拘留，四人家属连日来到湖南省公安厅、检察院门前抗议非法关押。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>晚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>点，自称办案警察（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18874861192</span><span>）电话通知朱孝顶律师，刘华已被批准逮捕，罪名是妨害公务。朱孝顶问律师何时可以会见？该警察回答做不了主，律师会见须找长沙市公安局专案组组长批准。律师问市局专案组组长是谁？警察答不知道并挂电话。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>日</span><span>，访民吴莎回到家，发现门口贴了一张长沙市芙蓉区公安分局发出的对（吴莎丈夫）邓生记的逮捕通知书，签发时间为</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>日</span><span>。吴莎表示，邓生记已被关押了三十多天，刑拘通知书，逮捕通知书，为什么都没有办案民警的签字，没有办案时间，这程序合法吗？公安局办案民警怕什么？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日</span><span>，长沙访民李香表示，有不明身份的人去李颂明（李香丈夫）家里威逼他老父亲，签没有任何法律效益的逮捕证。李香说，这些人视党纪国法而不顾，滥用司法权，如果没有权力的制衡，极权就会用来杀人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>参见：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/12/blog-post_6184.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/12/blog-post_6184.html</a></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-IzuTrA4NiKo/UMWXjuZQeYI/AAAAAAAAVwQ/06pcUQQsk8w/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-IzuTrA4NiKo/UMWXjuZQeYI/AAAAAAAAVwQ/06pcUQQsk8w/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"220\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/--bhOjGgfnc4/UMWXkhOZOhI/AAAAAAAAVwU/qfESB16FbKg/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/--bhOjGgfnc4/UMWXkhOZOhI/AAAAAAAAVwU/qfESB16FbKg/s1600/2.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-578551101067553194?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}